      "author_association" : "CONTRIBUTOR",
      "body" : "Concept ACK, but I think PR description should be clearer. Also, I think it would be better to drop the first commit 42688109b38063902f4c2621db3e465a3c9b2218 here, and substitute commit b00c0c2a73b3c443f78b74eee60ff3e401b0269f from #24306. Main reason is that I think it is confusing to have separate `GetPathArg` and `GetFileArg` methods which are exactly the same except one strips trailing slashes and one doesn't. I don't think it's likely we will have a need for the one which preserves trailing slashes. The commit from the other PR also adds unit test coverage.",
